Part.Source: <BODY bottomMargin="0" rightMargin="0" leftMargin="0" class="Form" topMargin="0"><gxgxui.Settings RevertTablePaddingReset="True" Language="Spanish / Castilian" InitialState="&gxuiState" RevertTableSpacingReset="True" ControlName="gxui_Settings1" /><gxGrid SflRender="gxui.GridExtension" MaxRows="8" ControlName="Grid1" GxObjClass="13"><gxColumn ColAttId="CustomerId" /><gxColumn ColAttId="CustomerName" /><gxColumn ColAttId="CustomerAddress" /></gxGrid></BODY>
parm(in: &UserId);

Do 'Init' Do 'Save' Do 'Response'
Sub 'Init' &data = &request.GetVariable(!'data') &matches = &data.Matches(!'{"name":"([^"]*)","value":"([^"]*)"}') For &match in &matches If &match.Groups.Count = 2 &state = new() &state.name = &match.Groups.Item(1) &state.value = &match.Groups.Item(2) &states.Add(&state) EndIf Endfor EndSub
Sub 'Save' For &state in &states For each UserId UserGxUIStateId Where UserId = &UserId Where UserGxUIStateId = &state.name If &state.value = !'undefined' Delete Else UserGxUIStateValue = &state.value Endif When none If &state.value <> !'undefined' New UserId = &UserId UserGxUIStateId = &state.name UserGxUIStateValue = &state.value EndNew Endif Endfor Endfor EndSub
Sub 'Response' &response.AddHeader(!"Content-Type", !"application/json") &response.AddString(!'{success: true}') EndSub
parm(in: &UserId);
